IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User info@nvc.sg
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -w -a info@nvc.sg -s mbsync-gmail 2>/dev/null"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Sync All
Expunge Both
